description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 7, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 14, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 5 for East, 8 for South, and 5 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40072-45852-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [14 Votes, Common]
